  "description": "Apex enum patterns \u2014 enum-based dispatch instead of string switching, ordinal stability, enum values in Custom Metadata, package-global enums, and the limitations (no methods on enum constants, no associated data). Covers `Enum.values()`, `valueOf(String)` failures, and the right way to map an enum to/from a picklist value. NOT for picklist-field design (use admin/picklist-design).",
